 Linkin Park 在汉堡首演新歌《Heavy Is The Crown》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/linkin-park-debut-new-song-heavy-is-the-crown-in-hamburg-3796007?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=linkin-park-debut-新歌重是汉堡的王冠Surej SinghMon, 23 Sep 2024 02:18:52 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3796007 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/linkin-park-hamburg@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Linkin Park 于 2024 年在汉堡演出" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/linkin-park-hamburg@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/linkin-park-hamburg@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/linkin-park-hamburg@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/linkin-park-hamburg@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/linkin-park-hamburg@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/linkin-park-hamburg@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这是他们即将发行的专辑“From Zero”的第二次预览</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/linkin-park-debut-new-song-heavy-is-the-crown-in-hamburg-3796007">Linkin Park 在汉堡首次亮相后的新歌《Heavy Is The Crown》</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/linkin-park-hamburg@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Linkin Park 于 2024 年在汉堡演出" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/linkin-park-hamburg@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/linkin-park-hamburg@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/linkin-park-hamburg@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/linkin-park-hamburg@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/linkin-park-hamburg@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/linkin-park-hamburg@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/linkin-park">Linkin Park</a>在汉堡演出期间首次推出了一首新歌《Heavy Is The Crown》——请观看下面的表演。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/linkin-park-new-singer-emily-armstrong-chester-bennington-from-zero-3791172">“这不是结束，这不是开始”：林肯公园以新面孔展望未来</a></strong></li></ul><p>昨晚（9 月 22 日）在德国汉堡演出时，乐队表演了《Heavy Is The Crown》，这是他们即将推出的复出专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/linkin-park-announce-new-singer-album-and-world-tour-3791116">From Zero</a> 》中的第二首歌曲。</p><p> 《Heavy Is The Crown》以有力的即兴重复段开头，随后是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mike-shinoda">迈克·信田 (Mike Shinoda)</a>的说唱诗句。它还包含新歌手艾米丽·阿姆斯特朗的漫长尖叫声。您可以在下面观看新歌的粉丝镜头。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Linkin Park - Heavy Is The Crown 汉堡现场首演" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Ql6UyFnm8rc?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> 《Heavy Is The Crown》是从乐队即将发行的专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/linkin-park-announce-new-singer-album-and-world-tour-3791116">From Zero</a> 》中删除的，该专辑定于 11 月 15 日发行（<a href="https://fromzero.linkinpark.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预购/预保存</a>）。这张专辑的主打单曲《The Emptiness Machine》是他们七年来首次发行。</p><p>本月早些时候，迈克·信田 (Mike Shinoda)、转盘手乔·哈恩 (Joe Hahn)、吉他手布拉德·德尔森 (Brad Delson) 和贝斯手戴夫·菲尼克斯·法雷尔 (Dave &#39;Phoenix&#39; Farrell) 在<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/chester-bennington-obituary-1976-2017-2113700">主唱切斯特·贝宁顿 (Chester Bennington) 不幸去世</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/linkin-park-announce-new-singer-album-and-world-tour-3791116">七年后重新组建了 Linkin Park</a> 。前死亡萨拉主唱艾米丽·阿姆斯特朗 (Emily Armstrong) 取代了切斯特 (Chester)，创始鼓手罗布·波登 (Rob Bourdon) 则被科林·布里顿 (Colin Brittain) 取代。</p><p>艺术家和粉丝们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rock-artists-react-to-new-linkin-park-singer-emily-armstrong-3791263">对新阵容的最初反应基本上是积极的</a>。然而，阿姆斯特朗似乎与山达基教和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/danny-masterson-sentenced-to-30-years-to-life-in-prison-for-rape-3494826">被定罪的强奸犯丹尼·马斯特森</a>有联系后，很快就引起了争议。在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-mars-volta">The Mars Volta</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/at-the-drive-in">At The Drive-In</a>前主唱塞德里克·比克斯勒-萨瓦拉 (Cedric Bixler-Zavala) 向这位歌手发送的消息<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/linkin-park-fans-re-share-cedric-bixler-zavalas-message-to-emily-armstrong-over-alleged-links-to-scientology-and-danny-masterson-3791311">在网上重新出现</a>后，这一消息被曝光。 </p><figure id="attachment_3791118" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3791118" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3791118" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/linkin-park-2024@2000x1270.jpg" alt="林肯公园" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/linkin-park-2024@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/linkin-park-2024@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/linkin-park-2024@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/linkin-park-2024@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/linkin-park-2024@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/linkin-park-2024@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3791118" class="wp-caption-text"> Linkin Park 与新成员 Emily Armstrong 和 Colin Brittain。图片来源：詹姆斯·明钦三世</figcaption></figure><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chester-benningtons-son-jaime-hits-out-at-mike-shinoda-for-betraying-trust-of-linkin-park-fans-with-emily-armstrong-3791931">查斯特·贝宁顿 (Chester Bennington) 28 岁的儿子杰米 (Jaime) 随后对筱田的言论进行了猛烈抨击</a>。后者解释说，歌迷可能需要“时间来思考”乐队与阿姆斯特朗的重组。他还表示，那些因这一决定而“不尊重”他的人将“反过来失去我的尊重”。</p><p>切斯特的母亲此后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chester-benningtons-mother-feels-betrayed-by-new-linkin-park-line-up-3795371">发表了一篇文章，指控乐队未能兑现通知他们乐队是否或何时重聚的承诺</a>，她写道，筱田甚至在切斯特去世前就计划用一位女歌手取代他。 。</p><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/linkin-park-address-founding-drummer-rob-bourdons-departure-3791129">创始成员 Rob Bourdon 离开</a>后，鼓手 Colin Brittain 加入 Linkin Park 参加本期演出。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/linkin-park-guitarist-brad-delson-confirms-he-will-sit-out-of-all-live-shows-3791566">创始吉他手布拉德·德尔森也缺席了该乐队的复出巡演</a>，但仍在幕后与他们合作 - 包括参与新音乐的创作。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/linkin-park-debut-new-song-heavy-is-the-crown-in-hamburg-3796007">Linkin Park 在汉堡首次亮相后的新歌《Heavy Is The Crown》</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
